sentence: Plus, keep in mind that P&G's dividends are only likely to grow from here.
P&G is a Dividend Aristocrat, having raised its dividend for 59 years in a row.
The bottom line is that while P&G's turnaround will take time, it is still a global leader in consumer staples, with a broad portfolio of very popular products.
For any investors wanting to buy P&G but haven't yet, now might be the right time.
